data.name: InstructionsText
data.value:
If you are hired, you will need to provide documentation in order to be eligible for placement. Please bring documentation to verify your identity and authorization to work in the United States. Please refer to the Form I-9 Lists of Acceptable Documents for the type of documentation that is acceptable. This can be found at www.uscis.gov/i-9-central/acceptable-documents. Please note that we need original, unexpired document(s) and cannot accept copies.
On the day of your interview, tap "I'm Here" to check in when you've arrived at the office.
Please let us know if you're Running Late by tapping the button below. Note, if you are more than 15 minutes late we will need you to reschedule for another time.
If you need to cancel your appointment, tap "Not Coming".
